$interpreted: Handsome Bear: Ohh~ Miss Rose, why do I always have tears in eyes?
Handsome Bear: That because my love for you just so deep...
Handsome Bear: You're like the sweet fragrance of spring flower...
Handsome Bear: ... I lose myself as I become intoxicated with you.
Young Master Bear: Shallow!
Young Master Bear: The gorgeous Miss Rose is no.1 beauty of all Bears. How dare you compare her to cheap lousy flower!
Young Master Bear: Sha~~ llow~~
Young Master Bear: Move! Should be something like this!
Young Master Bear: Ohh~ Rosey darling, if falling in love with you is mistake...
Young Master Bear: ... then I rather be wrong my entire life, just to have you.
Young Master Bear: You're like dazzling gemstone, shining so bright I'm unable to look you in eye...
Handsome Bear: Tasteless!
Handsome Bear: How could you compare Miss Rose's beauty to tasteless gaudy gemstones!
Young Master Bear: SHALLOW!!!
Handsome Bear: TASTELESS!!!
Young Master Bear: Who's that ugly bear? Why I never seen her before?
Young Master Bear: Why did she just walk into home of beautiful Miss Rose!?
Handsome Bear: Holy Bear, she so ugly my flowers are withering. Hope she stays away as far as possible.
Young Master Bear: Miss Ros...
Handsome Bear: Miss Rose, not only are you beautiful, but you're also kind and considerate. You're goddess reincarnate.
Handsome Bear: If I'm able to marry you, it's the best thing that will ever occur to me in my entire life.

Rose: Ara~
To be honest, I am actually not kind or considerate at all~
Young Master Bear: If Miss Rose is not kind, there are no kind females in this whole world!
Rose: I really appreciate your compliments. However...
Rose: I think I just heard someone calling my cousin Jasmine ugly?
Handsome Bear: That ug... That girl your cousin!?
Handsome Bear: What I mean is... she so cute, only blind Bear would call her ugly!
Young Master Bear: T... that's right. If anyone dares to call her ugly, I'll be first one to kick that guy's hairy a**!
Rose: With both of you being such gentlemen, I can rest assured.
Rose: Nevertheless, people always judging others from just appearances. No one bothers to properly understand her true self.
Rose: Therefore, I have decided to wait for Jasmine to find her partner first. Only then will I be willing to get married.
Handsome Bear: ......
Young Master Bear: ......
Young Master Bear: Doesn't this mean that if no one marries that ugly Bear...
Handsome Bear: Both of us can forget about ever marrying Miss Rose!?
Young Master Bear: Unless...
Handsome Bear: Hey, there really someone dumb enough to marry that ugly cousin?
Young Master Bear: Definitely. You'll see once you meet him.
Young Master Bear: In the past, he injured his head for some unknown reason, which turned him into complete idiot. Since then, everyone been calling him by his father's nickname "Dumb Bear Soldier.
Handsome Bear: After he marries the cousin, Miss Rose can stop finally worrying and marry me.
Young Master Bear: No, she's gonna marry me!
Handsome Bear: No, ME!!!
Dumb Bear Soldier: Whad are you guys doin'?

Dumb Bear Soldier: Owie owie~ Don't bite me...
Bad buggy, go away~
Dumb Bear Soldier: I already chased away bad buggy. No need to be afraid anymore.
Handsome Bear: That guy's Dumb Bear Soldier? Why he talking to plants? His head really okay?
Young Master Bear: That's just who he is. Perfect match with ugly cousin, right?
Young Master Bear: Hi~ Bighammer, it's been a while.
Young Master Bear: Dumb Bear! Stay where you are!
Dumb Bear Soldier: Long time no see~
Young Master Bear: Some nerve you got there! How dare you ignore me on purpose just now?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Huh? You called me?
Young Master Bear: I said the name Bighammer! Who else would I be calling besides you!?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Ahh~~~ Right~~~
Dumb Bear Soldier: Everyone's been calling me Dumb Bear. I forget Bighammer is name too~
Young Master Bear: Please at least not forget your real name!
Young Master Bear: W, what is that!?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Was fighting. Very hungry now...
Young Master Bear: Ewwwww~ What's this disgusting thing!
Dumb Bear Soldier: For me~? Can I eat this~? Thank you, little flower~
Handsome Bear: What a nasty looking fruit. First time I've seen anything like it.
Dumb Bear Soldier: You guys hungry as well? Here, have some too~
Young Master Bear: Stay away! I'm not going to eat something this nasty!
Young Master Bear: OW! That hurt, that hurt!
Dumb Bear Soldier: Little flower! No biting!
Young Master Bear: R... right. There's this Miss Jasmine we know who loves to cook. You can ask her to cook big meal for you.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Yippee, big meal~~
Dumb Bear Soldier: Then let's go~~
Handsome Bear: When did that ugly cousin love to cook?

Young Master Bear: Whatever, need to get those two to meet first. Then we'll figure out way to make them fall in love with each other, somehow. 
This way,  Miss Rose will finally marry me.
Handsome Bear: No, ME!
